<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:130%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:130%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(1) 해당팀장은 확인 및 평가된 환경측면의 평가결과를 생산팀장에게 통보하고 </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:130%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:130%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;검토된 기록을 관리한다.&nbsp; </SPAN></P>

