<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:180%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림체";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2.1 평가 시 고려사항 </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:180%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림체";'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:180%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림체";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(1) 정상상태, 비정상상태, 비상사태를 고려한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:180%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림체";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;정상상태&nbsp;&nbsp; : 공정 또는 작업상태가 정상조건에 따라 작업되고 있는 상태</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:180%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림체";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;비정상상태 : 공정 또는 작업상태가 정상조건을 벗어난 상태</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:180%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림체";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;비상사태 : 사고를 포함한 폭발, 화재발생, 천재지변 등으로 인한 환경오염이 </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:180%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림체";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;심각한 상태</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:180%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림체";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:180%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림체";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(2) 과거, 현재, 미래사항을 고려한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:180%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림체";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;과거 : 과거의 사고여부, 과거의 민원 및 불평여부, 공해단속 여부 등</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:180%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림체";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;현재 : 현재의 공정을 기준으로 유해성, 배출량을 평가</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:180%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-family:"굴림체";'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;미래 : 법령의 향후 규제치 예상, 사고방지를 위한 예방활동</SPAN></P>

