<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='margin-right:10.0pt;line-height:142%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:142%;'>6. 소음 및 진동운영관리</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='margin-right:10.0pt;line-height:142%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:142%;'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='margin-right:10.0pt;line-height:142%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:142%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;6.1 생산팀장은 현장의 소음 및 진동 운영관리가 적합하게 이행되고 있는지 환경 점검&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 및 측정 관리절차서(EP-1301)에 따라 점검한다.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='margin-right:10.0pt;line-height:142%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:142%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='margin-right:10.0pt;line-height:142%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:142%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;6.2&nbsp; 생산팀장은 운영관리절차에 대한 환경점검 및 측정결과를 기록으로 파악, 유지 </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='margin-right:10.0pt;line-height:142%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:142%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;관리 할 책임이 있다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='margin-right:10.0pt;line-height:142%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:142%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='margin-right:10.0pt;line-height:142%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:142%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;6.3 </SPAN><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";letter-spacing:0.1pt;line-height:142%;'> </SPAN><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";letter-spacing:0.2pt;line-height:142%;'>소음 및 진동규제기준은 환경법규에 등록된 규제치를 참고하여 환경 </SPAN><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:142%;'>목표 및 세부</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='margin-right:10.0pt;line-height:142%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:142%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;목표에 따른다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='margin-right:10.0pt;line-height:142%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:142%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='margin-right:10.0pt;line-height:142%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:142%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;6.4&nbsp; 환경방침 및 목표관리와 영향 재평가를 위하여 점검 및 측정자료는 집계 및 분석하여</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='margin-right:10.0pt;line-height:142%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:142%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;경영검토 시 보고토록 한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='margin-right:10.0pt;line-height:142%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:142%;'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='margin-right:10.0pt;line-height:142%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:142%;'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='margin-right:10.0pt;line-height:142%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:142%;'>7. 참 조</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='margin-right:10.0pt;line-height:142%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:142%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='margin-right:10.0pt;line-height:142%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:142%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;환경법규관리(EP-1102)</SPAN></P>

