<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'>1. 적용범위</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='margin-left:11.2pt;text-indent:-11.2pt;line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;본 절차서는 당사에서 발생하는 폐수, 오수/분뇨, 지하수, 흙탕물, 쓰레기</SPAN><SPAN STYLE='font-size:10.7pt;font-family:"굴림체";letter-spacing:0.3pt;line-height:165%;'>장의 침출수 등의 수질오염원의 처리에 대한 일반적인 절차에 관하여 기술한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'>2. 용어 정의</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;오수 : 사람의 일상생활과 관련하여 수세식변소, 목욕탕, 주방 등에서 배출되는 더러운 물</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;분뇨 : 변소에서 수거되는 오염물질(정화조의 청소에서 발생하는 오니 포함)</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;수질오염방지시설 : 폐수배출시설로부터 배출되는 수질오염물질을 제거하거나 감소시키는 </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;시설&nbsp; </SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;폐수배출시설 : 수질오염 물질을 공공수역에 배출하는 시설물, 기계, 기구 및 기타 물체</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'>3. 책임과 권한</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;3.1 생산팀장은 해당하는 경우 수질오염에 대하여 배출물을 감소시키거나 방지하는 책임</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;을 가진다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;3.2 생산팀장은 수질오염방지 운영관리 상태를 점검하고 측정하여 문제 발생 가능성을 파&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 악하여 필요한 조치를 취하여야 한다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:165%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:165%;'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:170%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:170%;'>4. 일반사항</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:170%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:170%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:170%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:170%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;4.1 수질오염 발생원은 다음과 같다.</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:170%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:170%;'><BR></SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:170%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:170%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.1.1 지표수오염</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:170%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:170%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1) 식당 및 화장실에서 발생되는 폐수</SPAN></P>

<P CLASS=HStyle0 STYLE='line-height:170%;'><SPAN STYLE='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:"굴림체";line-height:170%;'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2) 생산설비로부터 발생될 수 있는 폐수 등</SPAN></P>

